Usage: SET RATE_LIMIT_JOIN <pattern> [pattern2 ...]
  A space delimited list of server versions we should rate limit joins on.
  Unsetting this variable will disable rate limited joins.

Example patterns:
  hybrid-7* ircd-ratbox-*         Rate limit any hybrid or ratbox server.
  *                               Rate limit every server.
